Both flexbox and grid has its own importance and should be used for designing a web page.

grids works for 2D aligment

flexbox is good for space distribution

CSS GRID

grid column : the vertical lines of grid items is called columns

grid rows: the horizontal lines of grid items is called rows

grid gaps: the spaces between each column/rows called gaps.

grid lines: The lines b/w column//rows are called column/rows lines